				\begin{document}$${c}_{p}^{max}$$\end{document}cpmax optimisation, where the SC score is incorporated into an additional loss function, such that molecules with SC > 4 are heavily penalised and lower SC scores are encouraged. In Fig. 8b, we show that by constraining the dreaming process in this way, we can achieve a similar distribution of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
